rComments: She is an amazing and enthusiastic teacher. Very pleasant and polite woman that will break down ergonomical concepts until the whole class understands. Her knowledge in biomechanics also facilitated the learning of certain concepts. We were often challeneged in the class which stimulated porblem solving and alaytical skills

Prof from UofT's OT program - excellent prof for ergonomics. Great physical examples of theory and physiology, good use of personal stories/experience to add to learning of students. Interesting to listen to. Made the course work seem easy b/c explained everything so well. Lots of real-world applications. Very great prof. Online textbook (free!).
